  <ul>
    <li><strong>SHARE Approach (AHRQ):</strong> <a href="https://www.ahrq.gov/health-literacy/professional-training/shared-decision/index.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">ahrq.gov/health-literacy/professional-training/shared-decision</a></li>
    <li><strong>Curriculum gratuito de 1 dia:</strong> <a href="https://www.ahrq.gov/health-literacy/professional-training/shared-decision/index.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">ahrq.gov/sdm/share-approach</a></li>
    <li><strong>Calgary-Cambridge (referência):</strong> Silverman, Kurtz, Draper. <em>Skills for Communicating with Patients</em>. 3ª ed. CRC Press; 2013.</li>
    <li><strong>Materiais em português:</strong> poucas traduções formais; busca em <a href="https://bvsalud.org" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">bvsalud.org</a> por "tomada de decisão compartilhada" retorna materiais brasileiros e portugueses</li>
  </ul>

